{"tid":24212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦愛上咗人妻......","createTime":"2016-12-05T11:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T05:51:04.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8019492e6f68b6e2ad29c61946f9d125fe47c91f","tid":24212,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"我都知可能無人信我...<br />\n<br />\n我哋已經喺埋差不多兩年，原本啱啱開始咩都無諗真係好開心，到咗依家個關係越來越好，我發覺自己真係越來越愛佢，真喺好想同佢一齊，每分每秒都想住佢，我依家壓力越來越大，每一個夜晚我都好驚，因為我真係好驚夜佢會同佢老公做....因為我同佢都經歷過呢D激情，係激情之中真係覺得佢係我慨感覺，呢種感覺真係好溫馨舒服，就因為經歷過一到夜晚就諗佢同佢老公.....我知我作為契家佬唔應該咁諗，但真係太愛佢好難唔諗，雖然佢都好愛我，但為咗個仔同屋企人佢一定唔會離婚，我試過好多次壓力太多入咗醫院，跟著常試忍心分手，但最後大家都喺真心愛著大家真係分唔到，唉！我真係好辛苦有人明白嗎⋯⋯"},{"pid":"4eca3b2ec83963976b872563928af9786e0d4909","tid":24212,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"48歲(沉船)"},{"pid":"8f603d84e615a1f2deb3d760f9d3bcace9dfeac0","tid":24212,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"太太我喜歡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9251f0a398c26e9a145ee6f6e112847b1ff80c","tid":24212,"uid":7721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:59:24.000Z","msg":"48歲（淫人妻）"},{"pid":"9a478f05deecd64e13b653873ff33a6f9f24a9e7","tid":24212,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"call g解千愁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239c340762308de52ed751ae4555f64ad1064827","tid":24212,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太太我喜歡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經唔係因為身份"},{"pid":"f930b740628197d432b170ae41c9e63ab21f90bb","tid":24212,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73997.jpg \" data